OL,3,CFour-year-old 'excited' for first
OL,4,CChristmas at home after heart
OL,5,Ctransplant
OL,7,FITV Granada Reports correspondent Andy
OL,8,FBonner met with Freddie and his
OL,9,Fparents as they prepare his first full
OL,10,FChristmas at home after the transplant.
OL,12,FA four-year-old boy says he is
OL,13,F"excited" to celebrate his first full
OL,14,FChristmas at home after having a heart
OL,15,Ftransplant.
