OL,3,CFour-year-old 'excited' for first
OL,4,CChristmas at home after heart
OL,5,Ctransplant
OL,7,FHis mum, Harriet, said: "We've been
OL,8,Faway from home for the past two years
OL,9,F- it's been very different. Although
OL,10,Fthe hospitals make Christmas very
OL,11,Fspecial and magical, it's just not the
OL,12,Fsame as being at home with your family
OL,13,Fand your friends and being able to
OL,14,Fcelebrate how you want to celebrate
OL,15,Fthem."
OL,17,FShe continued to say: "Pre-transplant,
OL,18,FFreddie struggled with a lot. Even
OL,19,Fbreathing. He literally just suffered
OL,20,Fgreatly. It was really sad to watch.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
