OL,3,CFour-year-old 'excited' for first
OL,4,CChristmas at home after heart
OL,5,Ctransplant
OL,7,F"But now this transplant's giving him
OL,8,Fa completely new lease of life. It's
OL,9,Fjust lovely to see him doing what
OL,10,Fnormal children his age should be
OL,11,Fdoing."
OL,13,FFreddie's mum and dad, from Preston,
OL,14,FLancashire, are now encouraging people
OL,15,Fto talk about organ donation in young
OL,16,Fpeople because "children are not
OL,17,Fautomatically enrolled on the organ
OL,18,Fdonation register."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
