OL,3,CFour-year-old 'excited' for first
OL,4,CChristmas at home after heart
OL,5,Ctransplant
OL,7,FFreddie was part of the Waiting to
OL,8,FLive campaign which saw hundreds of
OL,9,Fhandmade dolls, based on children
OL,10,Fwaiting for an organ donor, placed
OL,11,Facross the UK.
OL,13,F"If you scan the QR code, it comes
OL,14,Fwith his story. It definitely made a
OL,15,Fdifference", Freddie's dad, Andrew,
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
