OL,3,CFour-year-old 'excited' for first
OL,4,CChristmas at home after heart
OL,5,Ctransplant
OL,7,FThe campaign aimed to highlight the
OL,8,Fhundreds of under 18-year-olds on the
OL,9,Fwaiting list for a transplant,
OL,10,Fincluding 16 dolls linked to specific
OL,11,Fchildren sharing their stories.
OL,13,FNine of the children who had a doll
OL,14,Fmade to represent them have now
OL,15,Freceived their transplant, while seven
OL,16,Fyoungsters remaining on the waiting
OL,17,Flist another year on.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
