OL,3,CFour-year-old 'excited' for first
OL,4,CChristmas at home after heart
OL,5,Ctransplant
OL,7,FIf organ donation is possible, parents
OL,8,Fwill be asked to make a decision as
OL,9,Fpart of their child's end of life care.
OL,11,FAnthony Clarkson, Director of Organ
OL,12,Fand Tissue Donation and
OL,13,FTransplantation at NHS Blood and
OL,14,FTransplant, said: "For many children
OL,15,Fon the transplant waiting list, their
OL,16,Fonly hope is the parents of another
OL,17,Fchild saying 'yes' to organ donation
OL,18,Fat a time of immense sadness and
OL,19,Fpersonal grief.
