OL,3,CFour-year-old 'excited' for first
OL,4,CChristmas at home after heart
OL,5,Ctransplant
OL,7,F"Losing a child is tragic and such a
OL,8,Fdifficult time, which is why we're
OL,9,Fasking parents to think about what
OL,10,Fthey might do around organ donation
OL,11,Fnow.
OL,13,F"Families tell us that knowing their
OL,14,Fchild has helped other people and
OL,15,Fanother family is not facing the loss
OL,16,Fof a child too can be comforting.
OL,18,F"We urge parents to think and talk
OL,19,Fabout organ donation for themselves
OL,20,Fand their children today. Your
OL,21,Fdecision could help save lives."
